   On the Net: State Election Commission statement:
http://www.gov.yu/e2000/index.html
</P>
<P>
   State Department:
http://www.state.gov/www/regions/eur/index.html
</P>
<P>
   Albright's comments to Senate Foreign Relations Committee:
http://secretary.state.gov/www/statements/2000/000926.html
</P>
