<HEADLINE> Canucks 4, Wild 4  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   VANCOUVER, British Columbia (AP) -- Rookie Daniel Sedin
celebrated his 20th birthday by scoring with 6:22 to play as the
Vancouver Canucks tied the Minnesota Wild 4-4 Tuesday night.
</P>
