<HEADLINE> Bulgaria Wins 58kg Greco Roman Gold  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   SYDNEY, Australia (AP) -- Armen Nazarian of Bulgaria pinned Kim
In-sub of South Korea to win the Olympic gold medal in the
58-kilogram class (127&AMP;frac34; pounds) of Greco-Roman wrestling Wednesday.
</P>
