   The blue-chip index got stung by a profit warning from one of
its components, Kodak.
</P>
<P>
   Today, the warning has come from the name-your-price Internet
firm, Priceline. But it looks as though the weakness in Priceline
shares will not spread across the market.
</P>
<P>
   Analysts say that's because the market appears oversold, given
its struggles in recent sessions.
