</P>
<P>
   The facilitator of business-to-business e-commerce saw its stock
rise after its chairman said the company's performance is
improving.
</P>
<P>
   Silicon Storage, up $1.73 to $27.75
</P>
<P>
   The circuit maker's stock rose after it said quarterly profits
will be above Wall Street expectations.
</P>
<P>
   Priceline, down $7.89 at $10.75
</P>
<P>
   The discount travel Web site's shares plummeted after it warned
that weak airline ticket sales would hurt its third-quarter
revenues.
